{"tid":2100944,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"銅鑼灣有間大酒店 - 邁克","createTime":"2020-07-09T11:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:57:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c47e81dde3a211436266d72545abcb51431eb858","tid":2100944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200709/20952069/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200709%2F20952069%2F&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmiHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d0b2f82e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200709%2F20952069%2F&h=b92539d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20200709/20952069/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣有間大酒店 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200709/large/1594201589_0608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200709%2Flarge%2F1594201589_0608.jpg&h=c6643a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n報載國安公署臨時基地設於銅鑼灣某大酒店，我一面讀一面深深惋惜：代表第二次正式回歸這麼重要的執政總部，應該徵用五星的半島呀，除了登上國際新聞夠體面，用最具殖民地色彩的地標整治殖民遺毒，戲劇張力之強諗諗都振奮人心，五星旗在昔日名利場前迎風飄揚，有種報仇雪恨的快意，共產黨威武形象盡收事半功倍之效，真是天設地造啊，人生路不熟的北大人唔知碇情有可原，港英政府訓練出來的鄭月娥肯定熟悉地方掌故，居然沒有殷勤獻計，試問該當何罪？別的不說，<br />\n............................<br />\n<br />\n家居隔離期間看光碟消磨時間，<br />\n............................<br />\n希特拉特派專員的「禮賓府」則設於歷史更悠久排場更架勢的慕利斯。 <br />\n<br />\n邁克<br />\n電郵 :heartsociety2@gmail.com"}]}